snippet.title: THEY WILL ALL REMEMBER I ATE THE SALAD WRONG - Saintess of the Golden Bow Build 1.01 - George Intro
snippet.description:
George is the Duke of the North. He's called cold-hearted by the Locari Empire Court, but to our protagonist he's surprsingly kind?!

Duke George Intro Scene - now updated with a CG and voiceacting.
Xander M. Grant - George
Veronica Laux - Celeste
Ariana Rosario - Penelope

Scene added to Saintess Polished Demo Build 1.01, now available on itch.
"Saintess of the Golden Bow" is an otome isekai/reincarnation visual novel inspired by Korean web comics.
